Global Digital Pupillometer Market Insights
Digital Pupillometer Market size was valued at USD 120 Million in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 250 Million by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 10.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Digital Pupillometer Market Overview
The global digital pupillometer market is projected to reach USD 674.0 million by 2030, growing at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 6.8% from 2024 to 2030. This growth is driven by the increasing adoption of advanced diagnostic tools in emerging markets and the integration of artificial intelligence (AI) and machine learning (ML) technologies into digital pupillometers, enhancing their diagnostic capabilities. The rising prevalence of eye disorders and the growing focus on preventive healthcare further contribute to the market's expansion. However, challenges such as the high cost of advanced digital pupillometers and the need for skilled professionals to operate these devices may impact market growth.

